 a homogeneous $d$-symmetry superconductor ; it is\nalso encompassed by several contemporary microscopic theories for the pseudogap\nphase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2015 17:06:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Jan 2016 00:12:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2016 19:21:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-26"}
