 operators $T_m$ and their adjoints $T_m^{\\ast}$,\nprovided $(m, N/d) = 1$. Lerch $L$-functions are characterized by this Hecke\neigenfunction property.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2015 19:05:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 Dec 2015 07:33:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 18 Sep 2016 19:17:15 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 31 Dec 2020 11:16:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-01"}
