avor of the warm Comptonization model in our sample of\nSeyfert 1s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2015 19:18:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Feb 2016 10:54:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
