articles decrease rapidly as the\nradiation altitude increases. Besides, the radiation prefers to be generated in\nannular region rather than core region, and this needs further validation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2015 06:38:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2016 07:15:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-18"}
