ower memory requirements. For all the considered classes of\ngames, we also study parameterized complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2015 09:49:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2016 12:45:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2016 12:24:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-22"}
